<!DOCTYPE html>

<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head runat="server">
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
    <title>电脑网站2.0支付</title>
</head>
<style>
     *{
        margin:0;
        padding:0;
    }
    ul,ol{
        list-style:none;
    }
    body{
        font-family: "Helvetica Neue",Helvetica,Arial,"Lucida Grande",sans-serif;
    }
    .tab-head{
        margin-left:120px;
        margin-bottom:10px;
    }
    .tab-content{
